  7,156,"Aru ya$ ise$ di ddunit, di laxeĂŽt; aql a$ nu$al ed $uĂŽeK\". Inna d: \"aĂąaqeb iW, a t SĂąaddi$ $ef win iyI ihwan. AĂȘunu W ijemmel yal cci. A t Aru$ i wid ipĂȘezziben, ipzekkin, akked wid iumnen s issekniyen nneÂŁ"
  7,157,"wid iteddun d Umazan, Nnbi ur ne$ĂŽi, i ufan iura $uĂŽsen di TuĂŽa akked Linoil\". IumeĂŽ asen d lqanun, Itekkes asen ayen n dir. IĂȘell asen lĂąali, igdel asen dduni. Ikkes asen aruz akked lqid nnsen. Ihi, wid iumnen yis, i t iĂąawnen, i t isellken, iddan d tafat id irsen yides, widak d imerbaĂȘ"
  7,158,"Ini: \"a yimdanen! Nek d Amazan n Ăebbi $uĂŽwen meĂŽĂŽa. Neppa, ineS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Neppa. Issidir, Ineqq\". Ihi, amnet s Ăebbi akked Umazan iS, Nnbi ur ne$ĂŽi, i iumnen s Ăebbi akked wawal iS. Ddut yides, amar a ppepwanhum"
  7,159,"Deg ugdud n Musa, arbaĂą iteddu s tidep. U syis ay pĂȘuddun"
  7,160,"NessemfaĂŽaq iten $ef mrawsin laĂąĂŽac, n leoyus. Mi s issuter ugdud is tissit, NweĂȘĂȘa i Musa: ewwet aĂ©ĂŽu s tĂąakwaz ik. F$ent ed segs mrawsnat tliwa; akka, yal amdan iĂ©ĂŽa anda ara issew. Nesbur iten s usigna, Nessers asen d lmenna akked ifeĂŽĂŽuoen: \"eĂ§Ă§et seg wayen ilhan, is ikwen N$at\". Ur aÂŁ dnisen, maca la ddennisen iman nnsen"
  7,161,"Mi pwanecden: \"zed$et di temdint agi, eĂ§Ă§et segs, ayen i wen ihwan, init: \"laĂąfu\"! Ăaddit di tebburt, s lekni. Ad awen NsemmeĂȘ tuccva nnwen. A Nernu i lĂąuĂ»am"
  7,162,"Wid idensen segsen, neĂ»fen awalen s wid ur nelli d wid i sen nnan. Nuzen asen tiyta seg igenni, ilmend n wayen ddennisen"
  7,163,"Steqsi ten $ef temdint i illan $ef rrif n yill, mi ur d rzin di ssebt, mi ten id usan iselman nnsen, walan ten, ass n ssebt. Ass, war ssebt, ur ten id ppasen. Akka ay ten NjeĂŽĂŽeb, deg wayen ssexsaĂŽen"
  7,164,"Mi d inna lois, segsen: \"iwumi la tepnabim agdud ara Isqucc Ăebbi, ne$ ara IĂąaqeb s leqseĂȘ\"? Nnan: \"d aste$feĂŽ ar Mass nnwen, amar ad ĂȘezzben"
  7,165,"Mi ppun ayen i$ef pwafekkĂŽen, Nsellek wid itekksen ayen n dir, NesĂąadda aĂąaqeb adiran $ef imednas, ilmend n wayen ssexsaĂŽen"
  7,166,"Mi sme$wĂŽen iman nnsen $ef wayen i sen ipwakksen, Nenna yasen: \"ilit d uddawen ucmiten"
  7,167,"Mi IxebbeĂŽ Mass ik, ard asen d Iazen ara ten iĂąaqben, s Ă©Ă©uĂŽ, alamma d ass n tnekra. Mass ik, s tidep, Ip$awal ar uĂąaqeb. Neppa, s tidep, IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  7,168,"NessemfaĂŽaq iten di tmurt, d leoyus, garasen wid imaĂąnen, garasen wid ur nemĂąin. NjeĂŽĂŽeb iten s ise$iyen akked tucmitin, amar a d u$alen s abrid"
  7,169,"NeĂ»fen ten, deffir sen, ineĂ»Ă»afen i iweĂŽten Tazmamt. Ppaddamen lerbaĂȘ n ddunit, qqaĂŽen: \"ad a$ semmĂȘen\". Ma rnan usan ten id lerbaĂȘ, am widen, a ten ddmen. Day ur Ăąahden ara s Tezmamt, ard tidep kan, ara inin $ef Ăebbi? U lemden i illan degs. Ppif axxam aneggaru, i wid ipĂȘezziben. Day ur tfehmem ara"
  7,170,"Wid iĂźĂźfen di Tezmamt, ipĂ©allan, s tidep, ur NveggiĂą arraz n lĂąuĂ»am"